<A>__{we're looking up at a fairly steep angle as louis staggers off balance. he steps with his other foot, misses, and goes flying.}
<L>__{exterior louis, closer}
<A>__{he does a half somersault in the air and hits the deadfall on his back, the green garbage bag flying out of his hand. his flashlight also goes. branches crack. white dust puffs out from under him.}
<L>__{exterior jud, at the base of the deadfall}
<A>__{louis thumps to the ground nearby. jud kneels beside him.}
